646
00:33:09,455 --> 00:33:11,722
Oh, I love Huell.

647
00:33:11,724 --> 00:33:13,490
He's the dearest, dearest man.

648
00:33:13,492 --> 00:33:16,560
[CHUCKLES] Um, do you mind my asking...

649
00:33:16,562 --> 00:33:18,695
