685
00:35:05,268 --> 00:35:06,767
[LOUISIANA ACCENT] Hello dere!

686
00:35:06,769 --> 00:35:08,769
Free Will Baptist.
Pastor Hansford speaking.

687
00:35:08,771 --> 00:35:10,437
Uh, who this?

688
00:35:10,439 --> 00:35:12,973
Good afternoon, Pastor.
