00:35:22,685 --> 00:35:23,984
Just... [FINGERS SNAP]

695
00:35:23,986 --> 00:35:27,954
I'm gonna step into the vestibule.

696
00:35:27,956 --> 00:35:29,656
- [SPEAKER VOLUME DECREASES]
